  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2> </h2>\n<h2>Add</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add confirmation before deploy build</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Design improvements for <span>Deploy Build page</span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span>Design improvements for Profile page</span><span></span>\n</li>\n<li><span>Design improvements for Activities</span></li>\n<li><span>Design improvements for Topbar</span></li>\n<li><span>Notify customer when image tag doesn't exist</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bugs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Elements were moving or blinking causing glitching effect when loading</li>\n<li>User should not be able to use the Build ID hammer icon to deploy a failed build</li>\n<li>The backup filename was not showing completely.</li>\n<li>Jenkins badge was redirecting to old Jenkins UI during Build phase</li>\n<li>Update links to Liferay Learn Site</li>\n<li><span>Invalid projectId string was not completely preserved across submission attempt</span></li>\n<li><span>Activities can't be read on IE11</span></li>\n<li><span>Service name missing in secret confirmation checkbox text</span></li>\n<li><span>The commit pill was being shown improperly when there's no commit available</span></li>\n<li><span>Some Services icon tooltips were not correct for the selected environments</span></li>\n</ul>"
      },
